It's no secret that away from the spotlight Kwesta is a doting family man. Earlier this week the rapper and his lady, Yolanda celebrated their eight-year anniversary together. Taking to Instagram Kwesta paid tribute to the queen of his heart. Even though the rapper is fierce when its comes to protecting his family from the pressures of the spotlight, he isn't shy to show his soft side. "In the form of a princess and a queen came my purpose in life," Kwesta said about his girls.